FT  12 DEC 92 / Finance &amp; The Family: Stewart Ivory launches unit trust - At
a glance
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Stewart Ivory is launching a unit trust in the increasingly fashionable
field of emerging markets. The trust will invest in areas such as south-east
Asia and Latin America and will aim for capital growth. There is an initial
charge of five per cent and an annual charge of 1.25 per cent; the minimum
investment is Pounds 5,000. There is a one per cent discount on the 100p
launch price between December 14 and January 10.
